Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩浆从魔界的入口处不断喷涌而出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日的勇者们是否也是在这样的地狱中一往直前呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}○联系你我○ 王都TV
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升 3000安培！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑是怎么回事 看起来有些年代了却如此锋利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 全A
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有多远了 加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事 给我让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是百感交集 时到今日 我反而如此像个勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好？我可一直以勇者自居
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔·斩击！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔 进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽 拉姆 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋 不要随便略称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干什么呢啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人守门的话 这群家伙就会一拥而入了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是勇者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要什么资格 你是个真正的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你一定要救出菲诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是… 你可是我看好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔·切萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 之后拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是吃亏不讨好的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 是个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可是上班时间 你在这干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙可担心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 一起回店里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺 你不记得我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔 你觉得本大人..成为魔王好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于老爸被打倒 不是有很多人都失去了工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有很多造武器和防具的公司都倒闭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说大家都很烦恼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 你完全没有必要成为魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会逃的 我一定要夺回你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}再说了 你表情也太冷淡了吧 我教过你接客的基本是笑容了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给忘掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非..常..感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 回忆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔法道具店雷昂王都店的店员 菲诺·布拉德斯通！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔 本大人我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒过来了吗 菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人为什么会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 劳尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住 菲诺！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人 不想成为..魔..王..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能放你去魔界！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳..尔..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 我不会让你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲..诺..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳..尔..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲..诺..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 不适合 那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲诺你不是一路努力过来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天一直努力着 我是记得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容 你的努力 全都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人无语般的乐观 但这又是多么地耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点点不甘心 又非常羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是 要成为一名独当一面的魔法道具店店员的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来！
